cs.CV, cs.RO, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.GR 

This paper is likely to belong to the computer vision (cs.CV) sub-category as it deals with image localization using deep convolutional neural networks. It may also belong to the robotics (cs.RO) sub-category as the method can be applied to robot navigation and localization. The use of deep learning also suggests that it could belong to the machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI) sub-categories. Finally, the paper may also belong to the graphics (cs.GR) sub-category as it deals with image synthesis and labeling from point cloud models.
